title: Plans approved for new self-build homes in Ladywell (Lewisham London Borough Council)
text: ( Source : Lewisham London Borough Council ) Plans have been agreed to progress new community led self-build homes on the Church Grove site in Ladywell . The new self-build development will contribute to our New Homes, Better Places programme,
